GM Isn’t in Talks to Sell Opel Unit, Handelsblatt Reports

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-06-14T05:31:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/gm-isn-t-in-talks-to-sell-opel-unit-handelsblatt-reports.html
General Motors Co. (GM)  isn’t in talks to
sell its Adam Opel unit,  Handelsblatt  reported today, citing a
person familiar with a confidential telephone call between GM
Chief Executive Officer Dan Akerson and Opel’s CEO Karl- Friedrich Stracke.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at 
 cperri@bloomberg.net . 